(
<figureCitation id="13193CA38413FFCC4DBA998BD4FBFA40" box="[159,248,1435,1460]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="16.[151,250,1371,1393]" captionTargetBox="[164,1421,202,1329]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1435,193,1350]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURE 12. Microtrichis pectana. A, habitus; B, side of pronotum viewed at 45 °; C, antennomeres 3 – 11; D, hind angle of pronotum showing seta x 1700; E, spermatheca; F, aedeagus; G, male ventrite H. mentum and submentum x 1320; I, underside showing meso and metaventra x 445; J, metacoxae showing fringe x 1800; K, male ventrites six and seven x 2280; L, antennomeres 10, 11 x 1700." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/241708/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="205">
Figs. 
